import React from 'react' import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome' import { faWind } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faMoon } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faSun } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faWater } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faEye } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faDroplet } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faTemperatureLow } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' import moment from 'moment' export default function Highlights() { const weather = useSelector(state => state.weather.weather) if(weather[0].length > 0){ let timezone = weather[0].timezone } return (

Todays Highlights

{weather.length > 0 ?

Air Quality Index

Deg

{weather[0].wind.deg}

Speed

{weather[0].wind.speed}

Sunrise & Sunset

Sunrise

{moment.utc(weather[0].sys.sunrise,'X').add(timezone,'seconds').format('HH:mm a')}

Sunset

{moment.utc(weather[0].sys.sunset,'X').add(timezone,'seconds').format('HH:mm a')}

Humidity

{higlights.humidity}%

Pressure

{higlights.pressure}hPa

Visibility

{higlights.visibility}km

Feels Like

{higlights.feelsLike}oc
:
}
) }
